column4: "Property `device` should be a valid IRI to an existing Device."
"Property `ipV4` has a min length of 7 and a max length of 15 characters"
"Property `ipV6` has a min length of 12 and a max length of 46 characters"
"Property `lastPingAt` should be a valid datetime (`Y-m-d` or `Y-m-d H:i:s`)."
"Property `lastHttpConnectionAt` should be a valid datetime (`Y-m-d` or `Y-m-d H:i:s`)."
"Property `lastSshConnectionAt` should be a valid datetime (`Y-m-d` or `Y-m-d H:i:s`)."
"Property `lastWebsocketConnectionAt` should be a valid datetime (`Y-m-d` or `Y-m-d H:i:s`)."
